wikipedia_page.main: Marianne Winkelstern (1910–1966) was a German dancer and actress. She retired and settled in Britain after marrying an Englishman.

response: The Big Attraction () is a 1931 German musical film directed by Max Reichmann and starring Richard Tauber, Margo Lion, and Marianne Winkelstern.Waldman p. 31
The Carnival Prince (German: Der Faschingsprinz) is a 1928 German silent film directed by Rudolf Walther-Fein and starring Marianne Winkelstern, Harry Liedtke and Hans Junkermann.Krenn p.79
